{"tid":1139643,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"『無論事情是否順利都能好好熟睡，第二天早上抱著「似乎會有好事發生」的想法醒來』","createTime":"2019-05-05T11:59:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T17:28:59.000Z","uid":76885,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"be277ed66eb46a4c85e4d6cb9f477be8f87f915c","tid":1139643,"uid":76885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T11:59:31.000Z","msg":"有無人係以下咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em>外在條件沒特好，卻很受異性歡迎？腦科學家發現，這種人有充足的「幸福荷爾蒙」</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.storm.mg/lifestyle/410746?f=cs&amp;fbclid=IwAR2o-v7MrKh6GKvRvetZPtm9YXD4VUR8JiuYPO1d42_5FYM3DGXgUe7vsyM&amp;srcid=7777772e73746f726d2e6d675f34383862633762666165356665333262_1557057272\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.storm.mg%2Flifestyle%2F410746%3Ff%3Dcs%26fbclid%3DIwAR2o-v7MrKh6GKvRvetZPtm9YXD4VUR8JiuYPO1d42_5FYM3DGXgUe7vsyM%26srcid%3D7777772e73746f726d2e6d675f34383862633762666165356665333262_1557057272&d=CFSJobiERGKWyjxxKHv2y%2Br6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=9cfb053d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.storm.mg/lifestyle/410746?f=cs&amp;fbclid=IwAR2o-v7MrKh6GKvRvetZPtm9YXD4VUR8JiuYPO1d42_5FYM3DGXgUe7vsyM&amp;srcid=7777772e73746f726d2e6d675f34383862633762666165356665333262_1557057272</a><br />\n<br />\n充實感所產生的「幹勁」，既不受結果左右，也不受他人影響。<br />\n就算沒做出任何成果，就算沒受到任何人吹捧，內心湧現的充實感也會讓人享受過程本身的樂趣。<br />\n無論事情是否順利都能好好熟睡，第二天早上抱著「似乎會有好事發生」的想法醒來。<br />\n<br />\n如果長期缺乏血清素的話，說不定會覺得「與成果無關？沒人稱讚也無所謂？那怎麼可能」，不過就血清素充足的人來看，拘泥於勝負、在乎他人評價而戰戰兢兢的心態，才讓人無法理解。<br />\n因為這種類型的人對於他人沒有客觀的評價基準，所以他們其實分不清何謂勝利、何謂失敗。<br />\n<br />\n明明不怎麼在意成果，那些一臉幸福的人卻收穫滿滿。<br />\n因為他們不會喪失幹勁、睡眠品質良好，所以仍然保有敏銳的直覺。<br />\n<br />\n看上去總是很幸福，很少出現劇烈情緒起伏的人，就算沒有特殊才華或突出之處，也能讓周遭的人感到信賴，覺得想和他在一起。"},{"pid":"c62a5d1c9ec09c58bdffc495feafd1fba69b5403","tid":1139643,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T12:40:46.000Z","msg":"係香港邊有可能有依種人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286d0b1c4a71281d7d982729498bdfa26a75aea9","tid":1139643,"uid":76885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c62a5d1c9ec09c58bdffc495feafd1fba69b5403","tid":1139643,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T12:40:46.000Z","msg":"係香港邊有可能有依種人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T13:12:48.000Z","msg":"其他地方呢？咩地方會有多啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf9db5a525fe7d64a73e8bb209f2d300770ac680","tid":1139643,"uid":31318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T16:35:34.000Z","msg":"可能係細個嘅自己？"},{"pid":"cbf64d91fb5d3cd86c46161a8bc6acac74b6eddf","tid":1139643,"uid":76885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf9db5a525fe7d64a73e8bb209f2d300770ac680","tid":1139643,"uid":31318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T16:35:34.000Z","msg":"可能係細個嘅自己？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T17:21:43.000Z","msg":"會唔會可以做返細個既自己？"},{"pid":"230f2814bae56ac63c81e4f65d6641d3b7952762","tid":1139643,"uid":31318,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cbf64d91fb5d3cd86c46161a8bc6acac74b6eddf","tid":1139643,"uid":76885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf9db5a525fe7d64a73e8bb209f2d300770ac680","tid":1139643,"uid":31318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T16:35:34.000Z","msg":"可能係細個嘅自己？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T17:21:43.000Z","msg":"會唔會可以做返細個既自己？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T17:28:59.000Z","msg":"好難<br />\n思想同處景都變咗"}]}